<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.4">
<l>vampavi ḻumtuḻāy mālai tōḷmēl kaiyaṉa vāḻi yuñcaṅ kumēnti</l>
<l>namparnam millam pukuntu niṉṟār nākari karpe ritumi ḷaiyar</l>
<l>cempava ḷamivar vāyiṉ vaṇṇan tēvari vara turuvam collil</l>
<l>ampava ḷatti raḷēyu moppa raccō voruva raḻaki yavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A tulasī garland, [its] fragrance wafting, was on his shoulders;</l>
<l rend="indent">bearing the conch and discus in [his] hands,</l>
<l>[As] a friend coming in our house, he stood</l>
<l rend="indent">- a refined gentleman, very young man.</l>
<l>The color of his lips was rosy coral; if [we] speak of his form, his was divine.</l>
<l>He was like an abundance of fine coral. Oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
